    "ncContentTypeAlias": "nC_WeSayWidget",
    "review": "<p>In 2 hours you will cover 20km of the Saalbach circuit including the Ski World Cup run, and the Hinterglemm circuit covers 24km of runs in 2½ hours.</p>",
    "author": ""
  },
  {
    "name": "Item 2",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "nC_WeSayWidget",
    "review": "<p>The Leogang circuit will give you 2½ hours boundless skiing pleasure during the 26km distance. The Tyrol circuit will take you into the neighbouring province on part of its 22km route in 2½ hours.</p>",
    "author": ""
  },
  {
    "name": "Item 3",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "nC_WeSayWidget",
    "review": "<p>You can enter the Skicircus via the Kohlmais lift in Saalbach and via the Reiterkogel lift in Hinterglemm.</p>",
    "author": ""
  }
]]]></weSay>
